model = keras.models.Sequential()

model.add(keras.layers.Dense(12,
                              input_shape=(6,),
                              name='Input_layer',
                              activation='relu'))
model.add(keras.layers.Dense(12,
                              name='Hidden_layer1',
                              activation='relu'))



model.add(keras.layers.Dense(1,
                             name='output_layer',
                             activation='sigmoid'))
